  "content": "# M3.4 Graph Edge Improvements — Implementation Plan\n\n### Task 1: Add `RustModuleMap` to `corvia-adapter-git`\n\n**Files:**\n- Create: `corvia-adapter-git/src/module_resolver.rs`\n- Modify: `corvia-adapter-git/src/lib.rs`\n- Modify: `corvia-adapter-git/Cargo.toml` (add `toml` dependency for Cargo.toml parsing)\n\n**Step 1: Add `toml` dependency to Cargo.toml**\n\nIn `corvia-adapter-git/Cargo.toml`, add under `[dependencies]`:\n```toml\ntoml = \"0.8\"\n```\n\n**Step 2: Create `module_resolver.rs` with `RustModuleMap`**\n\nCreate file at `corvia-adapter-git/src/module_resolver.rs`:\n\n```rust\n//! Rust module path → file path resolution via Cargo.toml + `mod` declarations.\n//!\n//! Builds a map from Rust module paths (e.g., `crate::config`) to file paths\n//! (e.g., `crates/corvia-common/src/config.rs`) by parsing workspace layout\n//! and scanning source files for `mod foo;` declarations.\n\nuse std::collections::HashMap;\nuse std::path::{Path, PathBuf};\n\n/// Maps Rust module paths to their source file paths.\n///",
